source.name: Total Wildland Fires and Acres burned from 1960 through 2012
source.description: Number of wildland fires and acres burned from 1960 through 2008 (updated annually). Includes federal (Bureau of Land Management, US Forest Service, National Park Service, Fish and Wildlife Service, Bureau of Indian Affairs) and state/local jurisdictions.  This information is supplied by the Department of Interior and the Department of Agriculture.
